{"tid":89020,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次整腦魔","createTime":"2017-01-21T05:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T14:29:11.000Z","uid":10172,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f0fcaa1fa3431542e098d37872ce12dc9501dcb","tid":89020,"uid":10172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"訂唔到腦魔既可憐蟲決定自己整比自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先落街文具舖同書局買不織布同手工棉 就可以開始喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdVASAFsHWyKZDpBcegk5DQUdVd4M8efZ11eD89fdtDMC?filename=ZQS9mJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQS9mJA.jpg&h=e6ce7265&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n布就4蚊a4size倒 買左綠黑紅黃 就係冇白色做眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唯有用t shirt剪<br />\n成本：$48 （棉花同部分布用到幾次所以之後整會平d<br />\n開始！根據以前中學學過整公仔既經驗應該要畫草圖先 然後剪出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUsotDoV3rrW3jrr9Ub4pGZUmT1aKh16RUCRmDK5TKQMX?filename=o9q7m92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9q7m92.jpg&h=d0c6568d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS4zsTXLkVtmLjJ2WEpiHBjUD1CPLGD8HXnvDthLENaQF?filename=ah3320F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fah3320F.jpg&h=6f6643e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n剪完就跟住佢剪塊布出黎<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/21/131002_fa28f7aef1840b36ea43b2bd5f8e3567.jpg[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F21%2F131002_fa28f7aef1840b36ea43b2bd5f8e3567.jpg%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=vbmn2%2BGBdo%2FsqVLC3OULdUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=b6821ac1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/21/131002_fa28f7aef1840b36ea43b2bd5f8e3567.jpg[/img］</a><br />\n然後開始聯埋一齊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/21/131224_88db5a7d4a3c14b030e701452fdc7e8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F21%2F131224_88db5a7d4a3c14b030e701452fdc7e8e.jpg&h=bb77a759&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma6j2zjJmYoQYvK6iNKSBTdnEoXdvuwkWJsKzBwTSqZ4R?filename=8B0h2ro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8B0h2ro.jpg&h=55468082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後塞棉花<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVgNUNayrGDWuEPJx5TEQH3Rn4uPn2cAXqoZtXca6PWJb?filename=fX82h1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfX82h1f.jpg&h=fdf51f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  中左少少幅射 不過唔影響大雅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc2QUyxNP5JeX2qv53WMuJ8SXgPosXnWjicwfaUKzvqxL?filename=pS7yQp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpS7yQp2.jpg&h=8fd2957c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾日後 唔憤氣 決定整隻冇幅射既腦魔bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用番之前既棉花同布 <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaoykNV9yPqpxXPcXGKmHnu6GxVM4c9qtAc4PhdF5xuHQ?filename=Z1DRdQc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ1DRdQc.jpg&h=8a9b2f79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUEu7HowGbcqvNf5YrZsM7ZUfbiWWtURaFRh9T9kb23qz?filename=WKo5V57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKo5V57.jpg&h=1163c65c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZj25QbJEoTCbi6GW73QeuesXXLpcWjTgL4HYQBAKhmZ6?filename=tY6Xk37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtY6Xk37.jpg&h=a0b8436e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR3TrPz4sUaH67FSdXMDyQsg1SRk8zjaBYZAzyPyiN1tG?filename=9a1KgQ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9a1KgQ8.jpg&h=f984eac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成！好似靚過上一隻 大家覺得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51933e36fffa90cefbf4c314304e657c091842a5","tid":89020,"uid":4085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"個頭大d就好睇d<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213333ea302bac76e6bc58d251299b45399fe565","tid":89020,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:20:06.000Z","msg":"輻射腦魔"},{"pid":"9296e46dc1460edc14e3dab6b55bf5ee2a3b75b3","tid":89020,"uid":4085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"覺得第一個好似靚d 第二個太瘦 大膽d試下攞多d位 唔洗岩岩好"},{"pid":"bc6879d4cee3259c48035fefff215348e908703c","tid":89020,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:21:36.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87116e25a8246776635764fb81501d2cd94ae48b","tid":89020,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"你想整立體 但個紙板係平面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   做乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812acb5b0718ff12c8c7060ff7bd1857f3aa0b08","tid":89020,"uid":67848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"試下將縫條邊嘅線收入去 會唔會好睇啲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee18c8be3ecf2b5d4540f9edf1e784430cc699cd","tid":89020,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05: