ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"紙樣係平面 公仔係立體<br />\n塊布有d位會變左側邊嘅「深度」<br />\n所以畫紙樣嗰陣要畫大d 避免變左第二次咁個頭太窄"},{"pid":"511fe9151310577192cf549389b7b402fc2e6e27","tid":89020,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絲打整隻比我,手工做既難得啊!!!"},{"pid":"120dfc8137ec7082caa9ad402a555a33764528cf","tid":89020,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd3dbcb2f8535be050df43b1e30e4eb3f420924c","tid":89020,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:26:55.000Z","msg":"好蠢.....你個板整闊d肥d"},{"pid":"653af32bac3ffe82c5f423cae96ccdbda2d99adf","tid":89020,"uid":35603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:29:11.000Z","msg":"頭髮呢"}]}